    {
      "id": "68",
      "name": "七聖召喚",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "プレイヤー紹介",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 2,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "協会認定プレイヤー。アアル村の雑貨商人。保守と臨機応変な対応を兼ね備えたプレイスタイル。どこで耳にしたのか、真実かどうか疑わしい「七聖召喚」の大会に向けて、せっせと準備を進めている…",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "冒険挑戦",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 2,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "「駄獣競走者？」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "ステージ紹介",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "様々な地域の商人たちが集まると、往々にして奇妙なアイデアが飛び交うものだ。例えば、ある人はこんな発想をもたらした。「もし、両足の生えたキノコンを飼いならすことができたら、荷物の輸送とキャラバンの護衛を同時に解決できるのでは」…その話はアザライの脳裏に深く刻まれ、彼の頭に強く残って離れなくなった…",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "相手の編成",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3913,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/06/18/132746206/13b5d195cff78e36f42705343488828a_4717230526318231158.png",
                      "menu_id": 19,
                      "name": "トコトコ水マッシュロン",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3371,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/29/132746206/44975ba6fc5a9efdc8d7f769125314db_2179215258469554732.png",
                      "menu_id": 19,
                      "name": "雷スライム",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3912,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/06/18/132746206/52ae2daf4762bc3cb4fc0a4ec84ed871_7653672650400559502.png",
                      "menu_id": 19,
                      "name": "トコトコ岩マッシュロン",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3913,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/06/18/132746206/13b5d195cff78e36f42705343488828a_4717230526318231158.png",
                      "menu_id": 19,
                      "name": "トコトコ水マッシュロン",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "開放条件",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "プレイヤーランク10を達成",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
